# Frontend environment

Copy to `.env` / `.env.local` for local work. Set the same keys in **Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables**.

```bash
# Required in production — Render backend URL (no trailing slash)
REACT_APP_API_URL=https://court-kiosk.onrender.com

# Must match backend KIOSK_API_KEY once that is set in production.
# Without this, kiosk write/LLM routes return 401 when the backend key is configured.
REACT_APP_KIOSK_API_KEY=

# Optional local override
# REACT_APP_BACKEND_PORT=5001
```

## Production checklist (Vercel frontend)

1. `REACT_APP_API_URL=https://court-kiosk.onrender.com`
2. `REACT_APP_KIOSK_API_KEY=<same secret as Render KIOSK_API_KEY>`
3. Redeploy after changing env vars (CRA bakes them into the build)
